00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:43,480
I want people to love me more, right?

402
00:31:43,480 --> 00:31:47,480
That is the worldly Christian, or the vibe Christian.

403
00:31:47,480 --> 00:31:53,480
The spiritual Christian starts to think more about the things of God.

404
00:31:53,480 --> 00:31:56,480
It puts the Spirit of God first.

405
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:59,480
Do you understand? 明白吗?

